Tennant first appeared as a [[census designated place]] in the [[2000 U.S. census]].<ref name=2000CensusCA/>

The [[2020 United States census]] reported that Tennant had a population of 63. The population density was {{convert|185.8|PD/sqmi|PD/km2|sp=us|adj=off}}. The racial makeup of Tennant was 56 (89%) [[White Americans|White]] and 7 (11%) from two or more races. [[Hispanic and Latino Americans|Hispanic or Latino]] of any race were 5 persons (8%).<ref name=DP1>{{cite web |title=Tennant CDP, California; DP1: Profile of General Population and Housing Characteristics - 2020 Census of Population and Housing |url=https://data.census.gov/table/DECENNIALDP2020.DP1?g=1600000US0678176 |website=US Census Bureau |access-date=June 4, 2025}}</ref>

There were 40 households, of which 15 (38%) were [[family (U.S. Census)|families]] and 24 (60%) were one person living alone.<ref>{{cite web |title=Tennant CDP, California; P16: Household Type - 2020 Census of Population and Housing |url=https://data.census.gov/table/DECENNIALDHC2020.P16?g=1600000US0678176 |website=US Census Bureau |access-date=June 4, 2025}}</ref> The median age was 62.5{{nbsp}}years.<ref name=DP1/>

There were 97 housing units at an average density of {{convert|286.1|/mi2|/km2|disp=preunit|units&nbsp;|units|}}, of which 40 (41%) were occupied and 54 (56%) were used seasonally. Of the occupied housing units, 35 were owner-occupied, and 5 were occupied by renters.<ref name=DP1/>

As of the [[census]]<ref name="GR2">{{cite web|url=https://www.census.gov|publisher=[[United States Census Bureau]]|accessdate=2008-01-31|title=U.S. Census website}}</ref> of 2000, the median income for a household in the CDP was $10,750, and the median income for a family was $26,250. Males had a median income of $21,250 versus $0 for females. The [[per capita income]] for the CDP was $9,929. There were 31.3% of families and 34.8% of the population living below the [[poverty line]], including 100.0% of under eighteens and 8.3% of those over 64.

100% of the population speaks English.<ref name="mla">[http://www.mla.org/map_data_results&state_id=6&place_id=78176&cty_id= Census 2005], 01-15-09</ref>

